Directory structure
===================
   test_2d_gc_cartesian         -- executable
   gcsim2d_cartesian_input.nml  -- input file
   README                       -- info (this file)
   run/                         -- output directory
   gcsim2d_cartesian.gnu        -- gnuplot script
   gcsim2d_cartesian_ref.dat    -- reference results

HOWTO
=====
0. Create output directory if missing, and move into it
     $ mkdir run
     $ cd run

1. Run simulation within directory
     $ ../sim_bsl_gc_2d0v_cart ../gcsim2d_cartesian_input

2. Run included gnuplot script
     $ gnuplot --persist ../gcsim2d_cartesian.gnu

3. Open *.xmf database with Visit (*)


(*) Make sure that the Xdmf plugin is installed!

